<div class="e-summary">
<p>A quick update on how the first couple of days have gone, in terms of getting the word out about <a href="https://ooh.directory">ooh.directory</a>: far more visitors than expected, far more new blog submissions than hoped for, and an interesting comparison between the effects of Twitter and Mastodon.</p>
